WEBVTT

36:32.310 --> 36:34.340 line:80%
Sir, what happened?

36:34.360 --> 36:35.530 line:80%
You don't know?

36:35.640 --> 36:37.800 line:80%
A man has died
after eating at Yixiang Restaurant!

36:37.800 --> 36:40.350 line:80%
His family came early this morning
to seek justice!

36:40.350 --> 36:42.680 line:80%
This Yixiang Restaurant is
nothing but a criminal den!
